−−−−−−−−−−→ Amygdala Circuit (FPGA
LUT) → Pre-wired Actuator Options
Latency budget: NPU inference ∼10 ms, SPI transmission <1 ms, FPGA LUT lookup
<0.1 ms, total pipeline ∼11–15 ms.
