3.4 Layer 4 — Pre-Wired Actuator Options
Terminal outputs are physical circuit states. Option om corresponds to a specific actuator
drive signal, hardwired at manufacture. FPGA output pins connect directly to actuator
driver circuits. There is no software-accessible bus between the amygdala circuit and
actuator outputs in the primary signal path.
